# ─── Catch-all for /blog/* that doesn't have a live equivalent ───────
# Covers the 14 un-migrated guide articles (see CONTENT_MIGRATION_PLAN.md)
# and any other legacy WP slug we missed. Landing on the journal index
# is better than a 404; visitors see the live content immediately.
/blog/*       /en/journal/      301

# ─── Old WP suites listing URL ──────────────────────────────────────
/suites-in-sifnos    /en/suites/   301
